Class Parcel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Parcel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    computesFee
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BOXParcel, FLTParcel

    public abstract class Parcel
extends java.lang.Object
implements computesFee
    The class Parcel is an abstract class that represents a Parcel object that has a width, length,height, and a tracker. The Parcel object can also add a list of items in the Parcel, as well as get the number of items inside it, and the total weight of the item. The Parcel object can also compute its destination fee, and insurance fee.
